job.title: Machine Learning Engineer
job.description: <p><strong>Job: Machine Learning Artificial Intelligence Engineer </strong></p><p><strong>Location: Pleasanton CA </strong></p><p><strong>Only open for W2 Contract NO C2C</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Must Haves:</strong></p><ul><li>Machine Learning, Deep Learning, NLP</li><li>TensorFlow, Scipy, PyTorch, OpenCV, OCR</li><li>Numpy, SKlearn, Pandas</li><li>Python, Spark, Hive, SQL</li><li>Productionize model.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>DELIVERABLES OR TASKS:</p><ul><li>The tasks for the AI/ML Engineer include, but are not limited to, the following:</li><li>Provide technical leadership, develop vision, gather requirements and translate client user requirements into technical architecture.</li><li>Design, build and scale Machine Learning systems across multiple domains.</li><li>Design and implement NLP algorithms</li><li>Design and implement an integrated Big Data platform and analytics solution </li><li>Design and implement data collectors to collect and transport data to the Big Data Platform.</li></ul>
